{"word":"H7170 - קְרַץ - qᵉrats - ker-ats' - Accuse","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">קְרַץ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>qᵉrats"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>ker-ats'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Accuse"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"குற்றஞ்சாட்டுதல், துண்டுதுண்டாக வெட்டுதல் - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"piece; denounce, slander, accuse maliciously, chew on (idiom)"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Masculine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (ஆண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> (Chaldee); corresponding to <a href=\"#/H7171 - קֶרֶץ - qerets - keh'-rets/7171\">H7171</a> in the sense of a <i>bit</i> (to eat the <i>morsels</i> of any one, that is, <i>chew</i> him up (figuratively) by <i>slander</i>): -  + accuse."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7127 - קְרֵב - qᵉrêb - ker-abe'/7127\">H7127</a>, <a href=\"#/H7129 - קְרָב - qᵉrâb - ker-awb'/7129\">H7129</a>, <a href=\"#/H7149 - קִרְיָא - qiryâʼ - keer-yaw'/7149\">H7149</a>, <a href=\"#/H7162 - קֶרֶן - qeren - keh'-ren/7162\">H7162</a>, <a href=\"#/H7170 - קְרַץ - qᵉrats - ker-ats'/7170\">H7170</a>, <a href=\"#/H7187 - קְשֹׁוט - qᵉshôwṭ - kesh-ote'/7187\">H7187</a>"}]}